# Account Deletion

If you need to request account deletion outside of the Quran: Hadith Companion App, please follow the instructions below:

1. **Contact Us**: Send an email to 'petvitalityservice@gmail.com' with your request.
2. **Verification**: Please use your email address associated with your Quran: Hadith Companion account to help us verify your identity.

We will process your request and provide confirmation once your account has been deleted. Itâ€™s our priority to ensure your data is handled securely and in accordance with your preferences.
